Rescue personnel have deployed a robot, to help them find little Khayalethu Magadla who fell into a manhole. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - It's been a difficult week for the Soweto-based Magadla family. Their six-year-old son Khayalethu fell into an uncovered manhole on Sunday. READ: Search continues for missing Soweto child Search operations have been underway, and a robotics team has been established to help with rescue operations.